debug nodejs by devtool

package.json
{
...
  "scripts": {
    "debug": "nodemon --inspect ./app.js", 
    "break": "nodemon --inspect-brk ./app.js", 
    ...
  }, 
...
}


$nodemon --inspect or node --inspect

$npm install -g nodemon -D


$npm run debug

Open Google Chrome and type
about:insepct
on Remote select target and click 'inspect'


NOTE: for typescript
$node --inspect -r ts-node/register ./app.ts
